        "localization": {
          "name": "Command & Combo",
          "description": "Targets 1 enemy, and another ally with the highest current TU. 500% damage to the targeted enemy, then gives that ally the next turn by reducing their current TU to 0. Unlocked each time the user damages an enemy with another attack. This skill is locked again after each use or if the user leaves the battlefield.\n\n- The given turn is granted after Counter Stance or Counter Skin type effects triggered by this attack, and so the affected ally will act before a countering enemy.\n- Active skills that grant turns cannot be used on turns given by this skill.\n- Effects that influence TU order may interrupt the given turn (e.g. Stuns targeting the lowest TU target).\n",
